{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/titleOverview.png?t=1736963049\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Inspired by arcade classics like Bubble Bobble and Snow Bros, Wispy Dreams delivers a modernized take on the beloved genre that fans have been waiting for. Bash enemies into each other with a variety of kicks, and watch your score soar as you chain them together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/merged.gif?t=1736963049\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/titleTheStory.png?t=1736963049\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Wispy Isles are in danger! A mysterious force is taking over the minds and spirits of all the land's creatures. Those you call &quot;Guardians&quot; have been powerless to stop it. Looks like it's up to you to restore harmony to the Isles, and perhaps make some friends along the way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/titleGameplay.png?t=1736963049\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The name of the game is to clear all the enemies on the screen to continue. But there's a twist - a magical key will appear and reawaken your foes. Bring it to the Gear Lock in time, or else you might get a visit from a not so friendly face. If you make it all the way to the world's boss, brace yourself for a tough fight. But wait, have you found all the secret items along the way?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/gif2.gif?t=1736963049\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/titleFeatures.png?t=1736963049\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 7 worlds to explore  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 20 enemies to pummel  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 9 bosses to fight  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 3 endings to discover  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tons of powerups to collect   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Loads of secrets to find   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Alternate difficulties and game modes to unlock   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lovingly hand drawn artwork and animation   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A beautiful and varied orchestral soundtrack</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/wallpape2.png?t=1736963049\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736963049","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736963049","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/0dc7f59a54fabd08d623bf4a27699a3cb3c833bc/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736963049","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/0dc7f59a54fabd08d623bf4a27699a3cb3c833bc/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736963049","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Full controller sup